Congo and northern Zambia to south-eastern Kenya and northern Mozambique. Includes Hall's greenbul (Eurillas virens [hallae]), named after the British ornithologist Pat Hall and which is only known from a single specimen taken in the Democratic Republic of the Congo. Hall's greenbul may be a melanistic form of E. v. zombensis. Description The little greenbul is a small bird reaching a total length of about 187 mm, with wings of about 80 mm and tail of about 77 mm. The upper tail and wings are brown, while breast and flanks are pale grey-greenish (hence the Latin name virens of this species, meaning \"green\"). The bill is brown, the iris is brown and the feet are light yellow-brown. Distribution and habitat The little greenbul is found in western, central and eastern Africa. Its natural habitats are subtropical or tropical dry forests, subtropical or tropical moist lowland forests, and moist savanna. Behaviour and ecology The little greenbul was the subject of a study regarding the impact of ecotones on biodiversity. References Andropadus virens. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 24 July 2007. BirdLife International Dr. G. Carmichael Low - Bulletin of the british ornithologist club – Vol LV.", "shortSummary": "The little greenbul (Eurillas virens) is a species of the bulbul family of passerine birds. It is found in many parts of sub-Saharan Africa.", "locations": ["撒哈拉以南非洲"], "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/98/Pycnonotidae_-_Andropadus_virens.JPG/960px-Pycnonotidae_-_Andropadus_virens.JPG", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-eurillas", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-eurillas-virens", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-eurillas", "species": "taxonomy-species-eurillas-virens"}, "expandable": true, "x": -327.17, "y": -330.0, "z": -277.35}], "links": [{"key": "bird-little-greenbul-2aee22c7__belongs_to_species__taxonomy-species-eurillas-virens", "source": "bird-little-greenbul-2aee22c7", "target": "taxonomy-species-eurillas-virens", "relation": "belongs_to_species", "label": "属于种", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 中的种字段补充。"}, {"key": "taxonomy-species-eurillas-virens__belongs_to_genus__taxonomy-genus-eurillas", "source": "taxonomy-species-eurillas-virens", "target": "taxonomy-genus-eurillas", "relation": "belongs_to_genus", "label": "属于属", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 分类字段补充：Little greenbul 属于属 Eurillas。"}]}
